      <content><![CDATA[<p>In order to edit model pages, open the <strong>Container pages</strong> tab in the <img dir="ltr" style="width: 14px;" title="searchBigIconActive" src="%(link0)" alt="searchBigIconActive" /> <strong>Create page</strong> dialog and select theÂ <img dir="ltr" style="width: 14px;" title="editIconActive" src="%(link1)" alt="editIconActive" /> <strong>Edit</strong> option from the Context menu of a new container page. You have to confirm this operation since you are about to edit the model for <strong>all new pages</strong>. This will not change already existent pages. This option will open the model page in the page editor, so you can add or remove default elements for new pages. Read more about model pages <a href="%(link2)">here</a>.</p>]]></content>
